        <p>
          <strong>Application Name:</strong> Nucleus Security for Splunk</p>

        <p>
          <strong>What is Nucleus Security:</strong>
        </p>
        <p>
        Nucleus Security is a risk-based vulnerability management platform designed to
        aggregate vulnerability data from multiple security tools, prioritize risk,
        and operationalize remediation across enterprise environments.
        </p>

        <p>
          <strong>Why This Application Exists:</strong>
        </p>
        <p>
        This Splunk application operationalizes Nucleus platform data inside Splunk,
        transforming aggregated vulnerability and risk intelligence into searchable,
        correlated, and analyzable enterprise records supporting remediation,
        governance, and compliance programs.
        </p>

        <p>
          <strong>Integration Type:</strong> REST API</p>
        <p>
          <strong>Data Format:</strong> JSON</p>
